    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine requires immediate attention due to significant oil leaks and a rough idle, and the transmission exhibits slipping in higher gears. Cosmetically, the body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling significantly. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and many of the electronic features, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. It will need to be towed or undergo major repairs before it can be considered a reliable driver.",
      "price": 5500.0,
